{"tid":2178004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國UFC選手Colby Covington 呼籲Lebron james 「若想改變社會請去當警察」","createTime":"2020-08-28T05:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T17:58:41.000Z","uid":28765,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d37ea0a2a097902d8e244402fe29bb7ea85a7eb9","tid":2178004,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"美國發生非裔男子布雷克遭到白人警察從背後開槍事件，引發NBA球員歷史級別的罷賽抗議，「詹皇」詹姆斯更在推特上要大家實際行動，「改變不是嘴巴上說說而已」，今天美國終極格鬥冠軍賽 （UFC）選手克文頓（Colby Covington）跳出來怒嗆詹皇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n克文頓是美國總統川普的堅定支持者，他今天在推特上發文嗆詹姆斯：「哇，你延遲了你的比賽啊？你想證明你真的想改變啊？那你就放棄你那幾千幾百萬美元年薪的工作、放棄打那種像小孩子一樣的又軟又特權的比賽啊！」<br />\n<br />\n克文頓最後對詹皇說：「請你自願降薪去做全美國最艱鉅的工作，成為一名警察吧！」<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3274296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3274296&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=4cf667cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3274296&h=4c774ea4\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3274296</a>"},{"pid":"21534ce4386c0779f87e4c8e3d1175ff064e3389","tid":2178004,"uid":332036,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T05:59:44.000Z","msg":"推唔到照推 左癌應滅世"},{"pid":"5c0d16fd9598466b1add1e85250a7fb19aa78a2d","tid":2178004,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e177dab1ff5f7be05139f9da135e3e451ead7d","tid":2178004,"uid":162103,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:00:55.000Z","msg":"Lick Beijing"},{"pid":"72636a3d8efea5965c89c28c9a6cee48391c7124","tid":2178004,"uid":4213,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"又軟又特權的比賽<br />\n<br />\n同連登仔一樣既觀點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad